Entry.JapaneseText: ……オレ、やっぱダオスが 優しい人とかって ぴんと来ねんだよな
Entry.EnglishText: I can't stop thinking how Dhaos truly is kind inside...

Entry.JapaneseText: だろうね、たくさんの人を 手にかけたんだもん
Entry.EnglishText: It's unbelievable, right? All those people he killed in cold blood.

Entry.JapaneseText: 私だってあいつに 初めて会った時、 やばそうなヤツって思った
Entry.EnglishText: The first time I met him I kept thinking he was a dangerous man.

Entry.JapaneseText: で、あいつのこと 襲った
私の父さんは、 ミッドガルズに 命を狙われてたんだ
Entry.EnglishText: He was responsible of killing my old man in Midgards.

Entry.JapaneseText: 昔、ダオスに滅ぼされた そういう名前の国が あったって聞いたことある
Entry.EnglishText: It was a big city in the olden days but I heard it was destroyed during the Dhaos war.

Entry.JapaneseText: そう、そのミッドガルズね
その日、私は森の中を 散歩してた
Entry.EnglishText: That day I was taking a walk in the forest.

Entry.JapaneseText: そん時にダオスと 会ったんだな
そう。で、あいつを 父の命を狙う刺客かと 勘違いして襲っちゃった
Entry.EnglishText: I mistook him for an assassin after my father's life so I attacked.

Entry.JapaneseText: え！？ だいじょーぶだったのか！？
全然。 ダオスの反撃食らって、 私、気を失って
Entry.EnglishText: It was fine. He counterattacked but I was just knocked out cold.

Entry.JapaneseText: 気付いたら、ダオス、 私に法術っぽい癒しの術を かけてくれてた
Entry.EnglishText: When I regained consciousness there he was. Using the Divine Power to cast a healing spell on my wounds.

Entry.JapaneseText: 今思うと、突然襲いかかられて 手加減できなくて ケガさせられたんだと思う
Entry.EnglishText: Thinking about it now, he probably didn't foresee my attack and instinctively didn't hold back. He probably decided the least he could do was heal my wounds.

Entry.JapaneseText: ゴメンなさい。 私、人違いしちゃった
Entry.EnglishText: I'm sorry, I mistook you for another person...

Entry.JapaneseText: 私はこの森に、 父さんと一緒に 住んでるんだ
Entry.EnglishText: I've always lived here in the forest with my father.

Entry.JapaneseText: ダオスは何も答えなかったけど、 私は一方的に自分のことを話した
Entry.EnglishText: Dhaos wouldn't answer to a thing I said. It became a one-sided conversation.

Entry.JapaneseText: それだけ。 彼は私には何も話さないまま、 森の中へ消えてった
Entry.EnglishText: Then without saying a word he left the forest.

Entry.JapaneseText: ……今のダオスと なんかイメージ違うね……
Entry.EnglishText: ...That sure is a different image from the Dhaos we all know...

Entry.JapaneseText: 私には今のダオスも あの時の延長（さき）に いるように思えるよ
Entry.EnglishText: I think the old Dhaos is somewhere deep inside the man we see today.

Entry.JapaneseText: ……人を……殺すことも 平気でやってたのに……？
Entry.EnglishText: ...You mean inside someone who can kill without batting an eyelid?

Entry.JapaneseText: 彼は正しいことだなんて 思ってなかったよ、きっと。 例え自分の故郷を救うためでも
Entry.EnglishText: I don't think he did any of what he did for fun. He always had his birthplace in mind.

Entry.JapaneseText: それがわかんないんだ
Entry.EnglishText: I don't know the answer to that.

Entry.JapaneseText: 罪を背負ってまでして 彼が何を焦ってたのか
Entry.EnglishText: I don't know what made him lose himself and be burdened with countless sins...
